**The Supreme Orthodox Unity Register for Beheading Malevolence, Red Register, Chapter Nineteen**

The Left Metropolitan Supervisor of *Qi* Libation Officers of Zhenhoucheng Abbey, affiliated with Water, located in Shina County, Hanzhou Prefecture, corresponds to the Chamber lunar mansion. Beginning of Winter, tenth month.

Disciple so-and-so of the Orthodox Register, whose fate is bound to the such-and-such Star Lord of the Northern Dipper, on this day enters the Dao, truthfully acknowledging past transgressions. Fortunate to have been born into the human realm, though unworthy of the pure transformation, I have acted with foolish obstinacy, mired in vulgarity and lowliness. From childhood to adulthood, I have long suffered from lingering illnesses, afflicted by wicked and perverse forces, never knowing a day of health. Now, I respectfully present ritual offerings and approach the gate of Master so-and-so to receive the **Supreme Orthodox Unity Heavenly Numinous Red Officials’ Register for Beheading Malevolence**, commanding its generals, officers, and soldiers to guard and protect me, so-and-so, in all my movements—coming and going, dwelling and resting—repelling and expelling all malevolent forces, capturing and destroying spirits and specters: *yuan*, *tuo*, turtles, soft-shelled turtles, foxes, ancient spirits, thousand-year-old demons, hundred-year-old monstrosities, hard and soft, pure and turbid, high mountains and deep seas, cunning and deceptive specters, the residual *qi* of the Six Heavens, the three *hun* and seven *po*, and all spirits that cling to the body’s gods. *As decreed by the Most High Lord Lao’s statutes and ordinances!*

Two **Heavenly Numinous Red Officials of the Beheading Malevolence Direct Bureau**,
Two **Heavenly Numinous Red Officials of the Beheading Malevolence Principal Bureau**.

