Thus concludes the swallowing of *qi* for the twelve hours.

Next, visualize the *qi* of the five directions:
First, visualize the azure *qi* of the East;
then, the vermilion *qi* of the South;
then, the white *qi* of the West;
then, the black *qi* of the North;
then, the yellow *qi* of the Center;
then, the twenty-four *qi* above the Grand Year Star.

First, visualize and swallow the *qi* above this day;
then, visualize and draw in the *qi* above this hour to swallow it.

Thus concludes the visualization of the *qi* of the five directions and others.

Next, visualize the *qi* of the five viscera:
The azure *qi* returns to the liver, governed by the Azure Dragon;
the vermilion *qi* returns to the heart, governed by the Vermilion Phoenix;
the white *qi* returns to the lungs, governed by the White Tiger;
the black *qi* returns to the kidneys, governed by the Dark Warrior;
the yellow *qi* returns to the spleen, governed by the Yellow Elder Lord.

Wood’s number is nine,
Fire’s number is eight,
Water’s number is seven,
Metal’s number is six,
Earth’s number is five.

